lead_paragraph: Wallabies winger Rob Horne has warned England they need to be wary of set moves from the fertile mind of Australia coach Michael Cheika when the two teams clash in Brisbane on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: England Must Expect the Unexpected in Brisbane, Says Horne
